    <footer style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(26,26,46,0.06); padding: 2rem 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--color-subtle); margin: 0;">
        <a href="/" style="color: var(--color-subtle); text-decoration: none;">TalkingToMachines.xyz</a>
        &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Questions? Reach out on WhatsApp or email.
